---
title: Goat's Cheese & Caramelised Onion Pizza with Balsamic Dressed Rocket and Walnuts
description: Looking for a tasty midweek dinner option? Try cooking up our Goat's Cheese & Caramelised Onion Pizza in just 20 minutes for a balanced and tasty dinnertime.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/goat-s-cheese-caramelised-onion-pizza-364238bb-15190586.jpg
